Package datasets

Interface IDatasetSample

public interface IDatasetSample
Interface defining the operations for accessing a single sample in a dataset. This interface ensures that any dataset sample can provide access to both its data and labels, as well as the paths to where this information is stored.

  • Method Summary

    Modifier and Type
    Method
    Description
    IData
    get_data()
    Retrieves the data portion of the dataset sample.
    Path

  • Method Details

    • get_data

      IData get_data()
      Retrieves the data portion of the dataset sample. This method returns an instance of IData that represents the data component of a sample.
      Returns:
      An IData instance representing the data of the sample.

    • get_label

      IData get_label()
      Retrieves the label portion of the dataset sample. This method returns an instance of IData that represents the label associated with the data of a sample.
      Returns:
      An IData instance representing the label of the sample.

    • get_data_path

      Path get_data_path()
      Retrieves the file system path to the data of the sample. This method returns a Path object pointing to the location of the sample's data on the file system.
      Returns:
      A Path object representing the location of the data file for the sample.

    • get_label_path

      Path get_label_path()
      Retrieves the file system path to the label of the sample. This method returns a Path object pointing to the location of the sample's label on the file system.
      Returns:
      A Path object representing the location of the label file for the sample.
